trans-unit.source: Specifies the HTML attributes that an <xref href="System.Web.UI.HtmlTextWriter"></xref> or <xref href="System.Web.UI.Html32TextWriter"></xref> object writes to the opening tag of an HTML element when a Web request is processed.

This enumeration is commonly used with the following methods of the <xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlTextWriter> class: <xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlTextWriter.AddAttribute%2A>, <xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlTextWriter.GetAttributeName%2A>, <xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlTextWriter.IsAttributeDefined%2A>, <xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlTextWriter.RenderBeginTag%2A>.
Specifies that the HTML `abbr` attribute be written to the tag.
